style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180706131834uXSdjrh5HwFGJeY0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807061318445FnySqPNQeKjYW4s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180706131851LBT8O9tH5nusg7ih.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180706131902AFmwPg4NdQTsaCOG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180706131910cS9Ur3wQthxX5F6Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图为 <a href=\"http://purple.fr/diary/jean-paul-gaultier-haute-couture-fw-2018-show-hq-jean-paul-gaultier-paris/\" rel=\"nofollow\">JEAN PAUL GAULTIER HAUTE COUTURE F/W 2018</a></p>"}